codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand latin grammar. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. \'Salūtābat\' nōn tempus praesēns, sed tempus ~ est; \'salūtāvit\' quoque tempus ~ est. Choose from this set of possible answers [ praeteritum praeteritum, imperfectum, perfectum] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-davinci-001' where ANSWER in [ 'praeteritum praeteritum', 'imperfectum', 'perfectum']
